OL,3,CWorkplaces must change attitudes to
OL,4,Cneurodiversity, says chef Heston
OL,5,CBlumenthal
OL,7,FHeston Blumenthal has called for a
OL,8,Fchange in attitudes to neurodiversity
OL,9,Fin the workplace after being diagnosed
OL,10,Fas bipolar.
OL,12,FThe esteemed chef and restaurateur
OL,13,Fsaid he was diagnosed with the mental
OL,14,Fhealth condition in recent months,
OL,15,Fafter previously receiving a positive
OL,16,Fassessment for attention deficit
OL,17,Fhyperactivity disorder (ADHD) in 2017.
