OL,3,CWorkplaces must change attitudes to
OL,4,Cneurodiversity, says chef Heston
OL,5,CBlumenthal
OL,7,FHe said he believes his
OL,8,Fneurodivergence is closely linked to
OL,9,Fhis business success and hopes this
OL,10,Fcan be the case for more employers and
OL,11,Ftheir staff.
OL,13,FThe celebrity chef runs restaurants
OL,14,Fincluding the three Michelin star Fat
OL,15,FDuck, two Michelin star Dinner by
OL,16,FHeston Blumenthal, Michelin-starred
OL,17,FHind's Head, and the Perfectionists'
OL,18,FCafe.
