OL,3,CWorkplaces must change attitudes to
OL,4,Cneurodiversity, says chef Heston
OL,5,CBlumenthal
OL,7,FIt also found 47% of UK adults with a
OL,8,Fneurodiverse condition believe this
OL,9,Fhas made it harder to find a job.
OL,11,FA separate study he commissioned found
OL,12,Fmany companies believe they have
OL,13,Ffurther to go in order to feel
OL,14,Finclusive to neurodivergent
OL,15,Findividuals.
OL,17,FThe survey of FTSE 350 board directors
OL,18,Fand HR professionals found 37% of
OL,19,Frespondents describe their company's
OL,20,Funderstanding of its neurodivergent
OL,21,Femployees as average or poor.
