OL,3,CWorkplaces must change attitudes to
OL,4,Cneurodiversity, says chef Heston
OL,5,CBlumenthal
OL,7,FThe chef added: "My most artistic,
OL,8,Finnovative and exciting work is
OL,9,Fbecause I am neurodivergent, which I
OL,10,Fdescribe as my superpower.
OL,12,F"The world needs to move on from
OL,13,Foutdated and archaic
OL,14,Fmisinterpretations of perceived
OL,15,Fdifference, and embrace the
OL,16,Fopportunities neurodiversity presents."
